1
00:00:01,580 --> 00:00:04,630
Wow.
A change of clothes really lifts your spirits, huh?

2
00:00:04,630 --> 00:00:06,550
What are you talking about?

3
00:00:06,550 --> 00:00:08,550
Still...

4
00:00:09,090 --> 00:00:10,550
That outfit looks great on you.

5
00:00:10,550 --> 00:00:12,510
Oh, thanks.

6
00:00:12,510 --> 00:00:14,470
Alright, after class.
See you at the usual spot.

7
00:00:14,470 --> 00:00:15,600
Yeah.

8
00:00:15,600 --> 00:00:17,930
Today, we're practicing the makeup for the actual performance.

9
00:00:17,930 --> 00:00:19,810
Got it! See you later.

10
00:00:19,810 --> 00:00:20,940
Yeah.

11
00:00:22,650 --> 00:00:25,820
He's in a really good mood.

12
00:00:33,620 --> 00:00:36,410
Should I make it a little heavier?

13
00:00:36,410 --> 00:00:40,790
(Yuki really loves makeup, doesn't he?)

14
00:00:40,790 --> 00:00:44,040
Okay, I'll do the eye makeup like this.

15
00:00:44,040 --> 00:00:46,000
Yuki, don't you have work today?

16
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:47,920
Why the sudden question?

17
00:00:48,630 --> 00:00:50,590
Because it's getting late.

18
00:00:50,590 --> 00:00:54,260
Oh, you're right.
Why didn't you tell me sooner?

19
00:00:54,260 --> 00:00:56,100
I couldn't. You were so focused.

20
00:00:56,100 --> 00:01:00,560
I gotta pack up and get going.
I'll get yelled at if I'm caught.

21
00:01:00,560 --> 00:01:02,770
After all, we don't have permission to be here.

22
00:01:02,770 --> 00:01:03,860
Right.

23
00:01:05,190 --> 00:01:07,110
I think someone's coming.

24
00:01:07,110 --> 00:01:08,940
I'll turn off the lights.

25
00:01:12,910 --> 00:01:14,950
Hide over there.

26
00:01:19,950 --> 00:01:21,920
Hey, is this even going to work?

27
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:25,000
Shh...!

28
00:01:25,750 --> 00:01:27,800
I think they're gone now, right?

29
00:01:27,800 --> 00:01:31,010
Let's wait until the footsteps are further away,
then we'll go.

30
00:01:32,340 --> 00:01:34,800
Hey, Makoto...?

31
00:01:34,800 --> 00:01:36,050
Yeah?

32
00:01:36,050 --> 00:01:40,060
You know, I really hate bugs.

33
00:01:40,060 --> 00:01:41,850
Oh.

34
00:01:41,850 --> 00:01:45,730
Um... that's not a bug, is it?

35
00:01:45,730 --> 00:01:50,190
Ah... I think it is.

36
00:01:50,190 --> 00:01:53,950
- No, no, no, no!
- You idiot, keep it down!
